=== Noun ===

'''election'''

#A process of choosing a new [[leader]] for a country where all eligible people cast a ballot to choose a leader or decide an issue.  The majority rules and the new leader is the one who has the most [[vote]]s.  There are variants, such as the [[electoral college]] system of the [[United States]], but the popular vote usually decides the victor.

